{"tid":1803463,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得刀劍四季好似講緊中國或者香港","createTime":"2019-12-30T08:19:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T11:58:21.000Z","uid":94794,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"aa74c61b00062ffe380bc00d6c702a6bc7b18d9f","tid":1803463,"uid":94794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:19:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DgtiO1x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDgtiO1x.png&h=262d0885&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係裏世界內，d人諗野要順從皇帝或教主，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一有自己諗法就會眼痛。<br />\n<br />\n若有自己諗法去到一個地步，就會自己拆隻眼，再去搞革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：諗多左"},{"pid":"b21453264ad3a83a0e4a1ce4ba8604adf05994e0","tid":1803463,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:20:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[極限挑戰] <span style=\"color: red;\">德國第三份聯署，最後48小時</span>，要多3萬人，連登仔做唔做到?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803447</a><br />\n<br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3Kka9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=2b8fb016\" target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5bd249b1b6817f667accd2d3073e5a018455ba8f","tid":1803463,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:27:46.000Z","msg":"唔怪得我屎眼呢排痛痛地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6620c687a69fa307fac7c34b71e9015db514ef3","tid":1803463,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:28:39.000Z","msg":"入面講緊嘅法律其實講緊我地一樣嘅野。<br />\n到底法律係咪必須遵守，係咪法律界定左呢個行為唔啱時呢個行為就一定係錯？<br />\n係咪政府無出不反對通知書而我地要遊行就係錯？<br />\n係咪當警察唔再執法時我地用私了就係錯？<br />\n<br />\n係咪法律無講咁樣係錯時呢樣野就唔係錯？入面貴族可以任意以懲罰為名搞女仔；係咪警察接受左命令開槍打人就係正確無錯？"},{"pid":"fa1e7ae11f38bfae4a19f6e6f5edc022e7294527","tid":1803463,"uid":336524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T08:30:41.000Z","msg":"結論<br />\n法律只係方便當權者統治嘅東西。我地應該用自己良知去判斷每件事是否合乎公義，而唔係靠法律黎界定行為是否合乎公義。"},{"pid":"2ba35f65d5016091dca8680a4c658c038f5d2958","tid":1803463,"uid":8307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T10:07:21.000Z","msg":"如果樓豬呢個post用巨人鋼鍊個啲<br />\n肯定好多清泉毒撚正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab351eb6291d9bc290b15265766324dc2162413","tid":1803463,"uid":94794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ba35f65d5016091dca8680a4c658c038f5d2958","tid":1803463,"uid":8307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T10:07:21.000Z","msg":"如果樓豬呢個post用巨人鋼鍊個啲<br />\n肯定好多清泉毒撚正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T10:53:09.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1964b6452cb0546c34625289ec64236f08b84c2c","tid":1803463,"uid":21456,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T11:32:40.000Z","msg":"有冇人覺得多啦A夢好似講緊中國或者香港<br />\n<br />\n香港好似大雄咁俾中共搶哂d野"},{"pid":"c55a805c7a2c0a8dc4b76ab60f142583290d8d4b","tid":1803463,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T11:35:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yNkZtcI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FyNkZtcI.jpg&h=f61a3275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nthis=樓主"},{"pid":"6d657a7dad52fe8f060d1fc9ad58067fdbbf9120","tid":1803463,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201